Reasoning: The paper discusses autonomous and adaptive systems, self-awareness, and knowledge acquisition, which are all topics related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The shift from design time decisions to run time decisions and the need for organic computing systems also relates to software engineering (cs.SE) and systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also mentions the complexity of interconnected systems, which could fall under distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). Finally, the need for learning in adaptive systems could also relate to neural networks and machine learning (cs.NE).
